data.description: This stunning Basement Ranch, located in the heart of Farragut, features 6 large bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, providing plenty of space for everyone. One of the standout features of this home is the impressive great room, complete with a beautiful stone fireplace and gleaming hardwood floors. The kitchen is equipped with all appliances, including a refrigerator, and boasts a center island and double pantry. Adjacent to the great room is a large den that provides access to the back deck, which overlooks the beautifully landscaped yard and saltwater gunite swimming pool.Four bedrooms, including the primary suite, as well as a separate formal dining room or office, are located on the main level. The lower level boasts bedrooms 5 and 6, a den/rec room, a third full bathroom, a laundry room, and a kitchenette that could be used as separate living quarters. Additionally, the 2-car attached garage offers a separate workshop area and a convenient dog washing station. This lovely home is located on a cul-de-sac and is ready for a new family to make it their own.
